KARACHI ,   Majlis-e-Wahdatul Muslimeen ( MWM ) on Monday announced it would hold nationwide protest on Friday against the killing of Sherazi Imambargah caretaker in Karachi .
A MWM spokesperson said that Shaukat Hussain was caretaker of Sheerazi Imamgarah and was killed in Methadar today .
He said that MWM condemned the murder of Shaukat Hussain and his guest Qaiser Hussain .
